\caption{Theoretical (dashed curves) and experimental (black dots) dependencies of the enhancement factor for Raman scattering from spherical silicon nanoparticles on their diameter D normalized to the excitation wavelength in silicon. Theoretical dependence consists of two contributions from magnetic dipole (blue dashed curve) and electric dipole (red dashed curve).}\label{Fig4}
